title: BRIEF-Premier Community Bank Of Florida To Join National Commerce Corp

organizations.name: brief-premier community bank of florida to join national commerce corp

text: March 20, 2018 / 10:10 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Premier Community Bank Of Florida To Join National Commerce Corp Reuters Staff March 20 (Reuters) - National Commerce Corp: * PREMIER COMMUNITY BANK OF FLORIDA ENTERS INTO DEFINITIVE AGREEMENT TO JOIN NATIONAL COMMERCE CORPORATION * NATIONAL COMMERCE - EACH SHARE OF PREMIER ISSUED AND OUTSTANDING WILL BE CONVERTED INTO RIGHT TO GET 0.4218 SHARES OF NCC STOCK AND $0.93 IN CASH * NATIONAL COMMERCE CORP - EXPECTS DEAL TO RESULT IN MINIMAL TANGIBLE BOOK VALUE PER SHARE DILUTION, WITH EXPECTED EARN-BACK PERIOD OF LESS THAN 1 YEAR Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
